{"tid":581206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廣深高鐵大停駛】列車故障狂等5粒鐘 深圳乘客：車站連冷氣都冇！","createTime":"2018-03-05T06:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T03:16:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3c53127e3a51b11372f3c6b4c305db48e5729f","tid":581206,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520232236_79ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520232236_79ba.jpg&h=1fea2eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520232241_2cbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520232241_2cbb.jpg&h=56ba3f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣深高鐵今日發生故障，從深圳北站到廣州南，或者從廣州南到深圳北的列車都出現嚴重延誤，部份列車延誤逾300分鐘(5小時)，有列車停在中途，乘客不適引發恐慌，而大批乘客滯留的深圳北站，在這時間壞冷氣，令到乘客的情緒變得激動。<br />\n<br />\n「今天的深圳北站到底怎麼了，列車這麼多晚點？」「廣州南出發到深圳北站的孩子們你們還好嗎，我坐的高鐵已經晚點了快一個半小時啦，中途還停車了&hellip;&hellip;」不少往來廣州、深圳的民眾，今日都被塞在路上，亦有民眾因為他們的班次嚴重延誤，在深、穗的車站苦待，部份人等逾5小時。乘客現場拍到的照片顯示，多班列車延誤逾5小時。<br />\n<br />\n「今天第一次遇見高鐵晚點，深圳北站的大部分列車都晚點，直接推遲了一個鐘！中午時這節車廂有乘客發病了，引起了不小的恐慌。」列車突然停駛，引發不少問題，雖然鐵路部門稱乘客可以免費退票，但有乘客稱在車站的退票窗口都被人塞爆，很多人都被困在深圳北站，剛好這時車站的冷氣故障，有乘客怒罵：「熱死了！」<br />\n<br />\n鐵路部門指出，因為「設備故障」，深圳北站的多班列車要停駛，當中包括從深圳福田至廣州南的G6522次、G6518次、G6524次、G6508次、G6528次、G6534次、G6526次、G6530次、G6536次，廣州南至福田的G6523次、G6519次、G6525次、G6521次、G6531次、G6537次、G6527次、G6533次、G6539次，及佛山西到福田的G6529次。<br />\n<br />\n當局未有透露為甚麼高鐵需要停駛，但有被晚點的乘客向鐵路部門說：「聽說路上掛了個氣球！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180305/57906826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57906826&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3faEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=d47d31f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57906826&h=c8d3d1ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180305/57906826</a>"},{"pid":"b92438b1ff857ab76e7d8b0679db7f5df7366abf","tid":581206,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T06:52:16.000Z","msg":"膠鐵真係不了"},{"pid":"d62abcdcf7cab4314527a52603c02a300b8fedcc","tid":581206,"uid":89868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3769c92eab5c5f5f9ca0a5decdc9013b64ebf43e","tid":581206,"uid":77473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"高鐵？不了"},{"pid":"e03b7f14cc0e53a876e4df92887505a5180c0f36","tid":581206,"uid":38671,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"好先進"},{"pid":"aa1007b309dbdd5fa793fa45280664642334cd98","tid":581206,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"嘿嘿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b113e72d797e92ee75974fc5dd45b1f9797e66","tid":581206,"uid":158613,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"一定好撚臭"},{"pid":"3e906275bd3b1ffebee8243ba4f63b9ffce19453","tid":581206,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T06:58:41.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"25dbb1062dc94d267a772b070ca26a538b1ad515","tid":581206,"uid":511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T06:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806b1b54f0ba249e3a2001b18349e96229f34f9d","tid":581206,"uid":3457,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"46b113e7